  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>With half board option you can enjoy breakfast with stunning panoramic sea views in the <em>Colonna</em> restaurant between 07:30am-10:00am. Candlelit dinners are also served in this spectacular restaurant from 08:00pm - 10:00pm. </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
