  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The beautiful Colonna Resort is located in a tranquil location, only 2.5km away from the famous resort of Porto Cervo. It is home to one of the biggest seawater pool areas in Europe, giving guests a choice of seven pools and a whirlpool with amazing sea views. The hotel also has its own private beach and a terrace with panoramic sea views, where a relaxing and traditional meal can be enjoyed in the <em>Colonna Restaurant</em>. </p>]]></listingDescription>
